    researchFindings: ["Russian clinical trials showed Selank nasal spray reduced anxiety scores comparably to benzodiazepines without sedation or dependence.","Research demonstrated Selank increased BDNF mRNA expression in the hippocampus, suggesting promotion of neuroplasticity.","Studies showed modulation of serotonin metabolism and enkephalin gene expression in the brain following Selank administration.","Immunological research indicated Selank could normalize cytokine balance and support immune function in stress conditions.","Animal studies showed anxiolytic effects in multiple behavioral models (elevated plus maze, open field test) without motor impairment."],
